text: Ivashin (Russian: Ивашин) is a Russian masculine surname; its feminine counterpart is Ivashina, which is also sometimes used for males. The surname may refer to *Andrei Ivashin (born 1999), Russian football player *Marianna Ivashina (born 1975), Ukrainian-Dutch engineer * Victoria Ivashina, Russian- American economist Category:Russian-language surnames
title: Ivashin
